oAuth - Open Authorization

Authentication
  - Who you are
Authorization
  - Who can do what















User - > client App(BookMyshow) -> Authorization Grant Request -> Authorization Server(Google)
                  client_id
Authorization Server - > code -> client

Client -> code (client_id)- > Authorization Server(Grant Req)
        -> Access Google profile for this User

Authorization Server - > Access Token(sdssdf1234356546dsfsdf)

Client - > AcessToken -> Resource Server

Provide resource to client  (email,profile picture,etc)





